SAPO,is,a,Portuguese,Internet,service,provider,whose,main,web,site,acts,as,a,web,portal,featuring,a,directory,of,Portuguese,sites,SAPO,Services,provides,a,large,suite,of,web,services,and,applications,to,developers,worldwide,The,Sapo,Mail,API,provides,a,set,of,operations,that,let,developers,manage,their,contacts,update,the,list,of,messages,and,provide,a,direct,link,to,the,message,within,the,Webmail,sevice,The,API,uses,SOAP,protocol,and,responses,are,formatted,in,XML